<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AspireHub-<%= title %>
    </title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="hscGuidance.css">
    <link rel="icon" href="logo.jpg">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.7.2/css/all.min.css"
        integrity="sha512-Evv84Mr4kqVGRNSgIGL/F/aIDqQb7xQ2vcrdIwxfjThSH8CSR7PBEakCr51Ck+w+/U6swU2Im1vVX0SVk9ABhg=="
        crossorigin="anonymous" referrerpolicy="no-referrer" />
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet"
        integrity="sha384-QWTKZyjpPEjISv5WaRU9OFeRpok6YctnYmDr5pNlyT2bRjXh0JMhjY6hW+ALEwIH" crossorigin="anonymous">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="nav.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="footer.css">

</head>

<body>
    <%- include('../partials/nav.ejs') %>
        <div class="hscGuidance-container">
            <div class="hscGuidance-content">
                <h1>Career Guidance after 12th </h1>
                <h4>Explore your options, identify strengths & <br>
                    choose the right college/program.</h4>
                <br>
                <div class="ban-btn">
                    <a href="#group">
                    <button type="button" class="btn btn-success">Check By Groups</button>
                </a>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="oppourtunities">
            <div class="oppourtunities-content">
                <p><em>Feeling lost about what to do after the 12th? Wondering which course/college is best for your
                        future?

                        Our personalised Career Guidance after the 12th program includes:</em>
                <ol>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Course selection based on your subject stream:</strong> Engineering, Medicine, Law,
                        BCom,
                        BA, BBA, and many
                        other options
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>Guidance on Entrance exams:</strong> JEE, NEET, CLAT, CUET, UCEED and many more
                        including
                        specific university
                        exams
                    </li>

                    <li> <strong>College selection:</strong> Top colleges in India and abroad</li>
                    <li> <strong>Admission counselling:</strong> Application help for colleges and universities in India
                        and
                        abroad</li>
                    <li> <strong>Study Abroad:</strong> Assistance in profile building for foreign university
                        applications,
                        Transition & Visa
                        support.</li>
                </ol>
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="img">
                <img src="./image/guideBoy.png" alt="thinking" width="250px" height="300px">
            </div>
        </div>
        <div  id="group"></div>
        <h4 class="avail" >Available oppourtunities depends on the chosen group in HSC</h4>
        <div class="groups">
            <div class="group-box">
                <h3>Science - PCM</h3>
                <figure>
                    <img src="pcm.png" alt="Vision" width="300px" height="200px">
                    <figcaption>
                        <p><strong>Best for: Engineering, Technical & Research </strong></p>
                        <h4>🎯Top Career Options🎯</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Engineering (B.Tech/B.E)</li>
                            <li>Architecture (B.Arch)</li>
                            <li>Data Science, AI & Machine Learning</li>
                            <li>Merchant Navy</li>
                            <li>Aviation (Pilot, Aeronautical Engineering)</li>
                            <li>B.Sc. (Physics, Chemistry, Mathematics, Statistics)</li>
                        </ul>
                        <h4>🎯Entrance exams🎯</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>JEE (Engineering)</li>
                            <li>NATA (Architecture)</li>
                            <li>NDA (Defense Services)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
            <div class="group-box">
                <h3>Science - PCB</h3>
                <figure>
                    <img src="pcb.png" alt="Vision" width="300px" height="200px">
                    <figcaption>
                        <p><strong>Best for: Medical & Life Science Fields</strong></p>
                        <h4>🎯Top Career Options🎯</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>MBBS (Doctor), BDS (Dentist)</li>
                            <li>BAMS/BHMS (Ayurveda/Homeopathy)</li>
                            <li>Veterinary Science</li>
                            <li>Pharmacy (B.Pharm) , Physiotherapy (BPT)</li>
                            <li>Nursing (B.Sc. Nursing)</li>
                            <li>B.Sc. (Biotech, Microbiology, Genetics, Zoology)</li>
                        </ul>
                        <h4>🎯Entrance exams🎯</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>NEET (MBBS, BDS, etc.)</li>
                            <li>AIIMS (Medical)</li>
                            <li>ICAR (Agriculture, Food Science)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="groups">
            <div class="group-box">
                <h3> Commerce</h3>
                <figure>
                    <img src="com.png" alt="Vision" width="300px" height="200px">
                    <figcaption>
                        <p><strong>Best for: Business, Finance & Economics </strong></p>
                        <h4>🎯Top Career Options🎯</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>B.Com(General, Accounting & Finance)</li>
                            <li>BBA (Bachelor of Business Administration)</li>
                            <li>CA (Chartered Accountant)</li>
                            <li>CS (Company Secretary)</li>
                            <li>CMA (Cost & Management Accounting)</li>
                            <li>Hotel Management (BHM)</li>
                            <li>BMS (Bachelor of Management Studies)</li>
                        </ul>
                        <h4>🎯Government Job Opportunities:🎯</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Banking (IBPS, RBI, SBI PO)</li>
                            <li>Civil Services (UPSC, SSC CGL)</li>
                            <li>SSC (Staff Selection Commission) Jobs </li>
                        </ul>
                    </figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>

            <div class="group-box">
                <h3>Arts / Humanities</h3>
                <figure>
                    <img src="arts.png" alt="Vision" width="300px" height="200px">
                    <figcaption>
                        <p><strong>Best for: Media, Law, Administration, and Creative </strong></p>
                        <h4>🎯Top Career Options🎯</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>BA (Economics, Political Science, Psychology, English, History)</li>
                            <li>Law (BA LLB, BBA LLB)</li>
                            <li>Journalism & Mass Communication</li>
                            <li>Hotel Management & Tourism</li>
                            <li>Fashion Designing (B.Des, BFTech)</li>
                            <li>CFine Arts & Performing Arts</li>
                        </ul>
                        <h4>🎯Entrance exams🎯</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>CLAT (Law)</li>
                            <li>NID/NIFT (Fashion Design)</li>
                            <li>UPSC (Civil Services)</li>
                        </ul>
                    </figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="groups">
            <div class="group-box">
                <h3>CS & IT(Any Stream)</h3>
                <figure>
                    <img src="cs&it.png" alt="Vision" width="300px" height="200px">
                    <figcaption>
                        <p><strong>Best for: Software, Programming & Tech Careers </strong></p>
                        <h4>🎯Top Career Options🎯</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>BCA (Bachelor of Computer Applications)</li>
                            <li>B.Sc. in Computer Science / IT</li>
                            <li>B.Tech in CSE/AI/IT/Data Science</li>
                            <li>Cyber Security & Ethical Hacking</li>
                            <li>Game Development & Animation</li>
                            <li>Digital Marketing & E-commerce</li>
                        </ul>
                        <h4>🎯Certifications & Skills🎯</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Python, Java, Web Development</li>
                            <li>Full stack Development</li>
                            <li>Cloud Computing, AI & ML</li>
                            <li>UI/UX Designing</li>
                        </ul>
                    </figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
            <div class="group-box">
                <h3>Vocational/ SkillCourses</h3>
                <figure>
                    <img src="skill.png" alt="Vision" width="300px" height="200px">
                    <figcaption>
                        <p><strong>Best for: Practical, Creative & Technical Careers</strong></p>
                        <h4>🎯Top Career Options🎯</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Animation & Multimedia</li>
                            <li>Photography & Film Making</li>
                            <li>Event Management</li>
                            <li>Travel & Tourism Management</li>
                            <li>Fitness Trainer & Sports Science</li>
                            <li>Interior Designing , Air Hostess & Aviation </li>
                        </ul>
                        <h4>🎯Diploma & short term Courses🎯</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Digital Marketing</li>
                            <li>Graphic Design & UI/UX</li>
                            <li>Ethical Hacking</li>
                            <li>Web Development</li>
                        </ul>
                    </figcaption>
                </figure>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="To-Do">
            <div class="todo-container">
                <h2>Career Roadmap To-Do List</h2>
                <ul class="todo-list">
                    <li><input type="checkbox"> Identify my strengths & skills</li>
                    <li><input type="checkbox"> Research career options based on strengths</li>
                    <li><input type="checkbox"> Choose the right degree or diploma</li>
                    <li><input type="checkbox"> Develop key technical and soft skills</li>
                    <li><input type="checkbox"> Gain hands-on experience (internships/projects)</li>
                    <li><input type="checkbox"> Build a strong portfolio & resume</li>
                    <li><input type="checkbox"> Prepare for job interviews & networking</li>
                    <li><input type="checkbox"> Set short-term & long-term career goals</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="faq-box">
            <h2 class="vertical-box-h2"> Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ) – Career Guidance After 12th (HSC)</h2>
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>What are my career options if I choose the Science stream?</span>
                    <span class="arrow">🔽</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <ul>
                        <li>B.Tech/B.E (Engineering) – PCM Students</li>
                        <li>MBBS/BDS (Medical) – PCB Students</li>
                        <li>B.Sc. (IT, Biotechnology, Physics, Chemistry, etc.) – PCM/PCB Students</li>
                        <li>Pharmacy (B.Pharm, D.Pharm) – PCB Students</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>Can I pursue a career in IT without Mathematics in 12th?</span>
                    <span class="arrow">🔽</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Yes, some universities offer BCA (Bachelor of Computer Applications) without Mathematics.  
                    However, B.Tech (Computer Science) requires Mathematics in 12th.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>Which is better: B.Com or BBA for a career in business?</span>
                    <span class="arrow">🔽</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p><strong>B.Com</strong> is a general commerce degree, suitable for careers in Accounting, Finance, and CA.  
                    <strong>BBA</strong> focuses on management and is ideal for MBA aspirants. Choose based on your career goals.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>What if I don’t want to do traditional degrees like Engineering or Medicine?</span>
                    <span class="arrow">🔽</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>You can explore fields like Digital Marketing, Ethical Hacking, UI/UX Design, Data Science, Film Making, Aviation, and Event Management.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>Which government jobs can I apply for after 12th?</span>
                    <span class="arrow">🔽</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <ul>
                        <li>SSC CHSL – Clerk & Assistant Jobs</li>
                        <li>Railway (RRB) – Technician, Assistant Loco Pilot</li>
                        <li>NDA – Army, Navy, Airforce (Defense Services)</li>
                        <li>State Police – Constable Posts</li>
                        <li>Banking – Clerk Level Jobs</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>I want to study abroad after 12th. What are my options?</span>
                    <span class="arrow">🔽</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>You can apply for undergraduate programs in countries like the USA, Canada, UK, and Australia.  
                    Entrance exams like SAT, IELTS, and TOEFL are required for admission.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>Is Arts only for students with low marks?</span>
                    <span class="arrow">🔽</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>No! Arts offers diverse career options like Journalism, Law, Psychology, Graphic Design, and Foreign Languages.  
                    Many high-scoring students choose Arts for creative and high-paying careers.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>How can I prepare for a career in Artificial Intelligence (AI) after 12th?</span>
                    <span class="arrow">🔽</span>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <p>Opt for B.Tech (AI & Data Science) or B.Sc. (AI). Learn Python, Machine Learning, and Deep Learning.  
                    Platforms like Coursera and Udemy offer online AI courses.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        
        <script>
            const faqItems = document.querySelectorAll(".faq-question");

            faqItems.forEach(item => {
                item.addEventListener("click", () => {
                    const answer = item.nextElementSibling;
                    const arrow = item.querySelector(".arrow");

                    if (answer.style.display === "block") {
                        answer.style.display = "none";
                        arrow.textContent = "🔽";
                    } else {
                        answer.style.display = "block";
                        arrow.textContent = "⬆️";
                    }
                });
            });
        </script>

        <%- include('../partials/footer.ejs') %>
            
</body>

</html>